<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Arynwood — Classic View</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0e0e0e;
    --text: #c9c7ff;
    --accent: #b48eff;
    --link: #79b8ff;
    --link-hover: #b48eff;
    --box-bg: #121212;
    --box-border: #2e254e;
    --box-shadow: rgba(180, 142, 255, 0.15);
  }

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background-color: var(--box-bg);
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--box-shadow);
  }

  h1, h2 {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-shadow: 0 0 2px var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .section {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--link);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  a:hover {
    color: var(--link-hover);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    list-style-type: square;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .link-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .link-row a {
    flex: 0 1 auto;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #161822;
    border: 1px solid var(--box-border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: background 0.2s ease;
    min-width: 100px;
    max-width: 150px;
  }

  .link-row a:hover {
    background-color: #1f2130;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    text-align: right;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #888;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: #b9aaff;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
    body {
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }

    .link-row {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .link-row a {
      flex: 1 1 45%;
      max-width: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Arynwood — Home</h1>
    <p>
      Welcome to Arynwood — A portfolio and transparent coding hub for Lorelei Noble. Here you'll find links to my current projects, artwork galleries, and build logs. I document everything from front-end design to smart contract deployments — with style.
    </p>

